<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="113" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,469,998]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis box="[199,370,541,566]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
<collectingCountry box="[199,257,541,566]" name="Malta" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">Male</collectingCountry>
genitalia.
</emphasis>
Pygofer longer than height, obtusely rounded posteriorly with macrosetae confined to posterior 
<number box="[151,200,577,601]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="0.33">0.33</number>
length. Valve 
<taxonomicName box="[367,478,577,602]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Amaranthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="triangular">triangular</taxonomicName>
, 
<number box="[491,526,577,601]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="1.8">1.8</number>
times as wide at base as long medially, with conically rounded posterior angle. Subgenital plates with caudal membranous fingerlike process 
<number box="[857,906,613,638]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" value="0.35">0.35</number>
as long as total length, laterally with a row of stout spines and marginal long hairlike setae. Apophysis of style almost straight, transversely rugose, subapical lobe well developed. Connective with stem slightly longer than arms. Aedeagal shafts without basal process, divergent in basal half and convergent in distal half in posterior view, each shaft with gonopore at mid-length, shaft beyond gonopore ribbonlike, with rounded apex.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,469,998]" box="[199,938,793,818]" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">
<emphasis box="[199,369,794,817]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">Measurements.</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[375,433,793,818]" name="Malta" pageId="12" pageNumber="113">Male</collectingCountry>
<quantity box="[440,526,793,818]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" unit="mm" value="3.5">3.5 mm</quantity>
long and 
<quantity box="[636,736,793,818]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.15" pageId="12" pageNumber="113" unit="mm" value="1.15">1.15 mm</quantity>
wide across eyes.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
